<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Jin's Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>

        .big-desc { font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .sub-desc { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; line-height: 1.6; }
        strong { color: #000; font-weight: 800; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="side-nav">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#home" title="Home" class="nav-link"></a></li>
            <li><a href="#about" title="About" class="nav-link"></a></li>
            <li><a href="#portfolio" title="Portfolio" class="nav-link"></a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact" title="Contact" class="nav-link"></a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header id="home" class="magazine-cover">
        <div class="top-info">
            <div class="info-col"><strong>Jin:</strong><br>Backend Dev</div>
            <div class="info-col"><strong>Location:</strong><br>Incheon, KR</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-title">Portfolio</div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="about" class="section-container">
            <div class="about-wrapper">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 1rem; color: #999; margin-bottom: 20px;">About Me</h2>
                    
                    <p class="big-desc">
                        고객의 경험을 지키는<br>
                        <strong>무결성(Integrity)을 지닌 견고한 구조</strong>를<br> 설계하는
                        서버 엔지니어 <strong>서진우</strong>입니다.
                    </p>     
                    
                    <p class="sub-desc">
                       서비스에서 데이터의 가치는 고객의 신뢰와 직결됨을 이해하고 있습니다.<br>
                        <strong>CS 지식(OS, Network)</strong>과 <strong>자료구조</strong>에 대한 깊은 이해를 바탕으로,<br>
                        트래픽이 몰려도 중단되지 않는 <strong>안정적인 아키텍처</strong>를 구현합니다. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-photo">
                    <img src="/images/me.jpg" alt="Jin">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="portfolio" class="section-container bg-gray">
            <div class="portfolio-header">
                <h2>Selected Works</h2>
            </div>
            
        <div class="portfolio-list">
                
                <div class="project-row">
                    <div class="pj-img">
                        <a href="<%= projects[0].link %>" target="_blank">
                            <img src="/images/p1.jpg" alt="music" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/600x400'">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pj-text">
                        <h3>PR<br> 음악 스트리밍</h3>
                        <p class="desc">Backend Dev <br><br> 
                            로그인 / 업로드 <br>
                            실시간 채팅 및 소켓 통신 구현<br>
                            및 전체 작업 수행</p>
                        <p class="period">10.02.2025 ~ 11.30.2025</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-row">
                    <div class="pj-img">
                        <a href="<%= projects[1].link %>" target="_blank">
                            <img src="/images/p2.jpg" alt="board" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/600x400'">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pj-text">
                        <h3>PR<br> GUI<br> 게시판</h3>
                        <p class="desc">Backend Dev <br><br>
                            데이터베이스와 연결 <br>
                            게시판에 필요한 다양한 기능을<br>
                            JAVA 를 이용하여 구현</p>
                        <p class="period">05.02.2025 ~ 06.30.2025</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="section-container">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>mochayong@naver.com</p>
            <p>Last Updated: December 1, 2025</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script>
        const sections = document.querySelectorAll('header, section');
        const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    const id = entry.target.getAttribute('id');
                    navLinks.forEach(link => {
                        link.classList.remove('active');
                        if (link.getAttribute('href') === '#' + id) {
                            link.classList.add('active');
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
        }, { threshold: 0.5 });
        sections.forEach(section => { observer.observe(section); });
    </script>

</body>
</html>Contact